  hr
  a(name='install', href='#install')
    h4 Install a modern browser
  .alert If you sure that you have latest version of your favorite browser, you may 
    a(href='#configure') skip this step.
  p First of all, you should install full featured browser. 
    | Go to 
    a(target="_blank", href='http://whatbrowser.org/') http://whatbrowser.org/ 
    | and do it!
  p Seriously, you must do it for comfortable work and computer safety.
  
  hr
  a(name='configure', href='#configure')
    h4 Configure tortigra
  ul.thumbnails
    li.thumbnail.span4
      img(src='/img/lesson-2a.png')
      | Click on button 
      code Init
      |  on the header.
    li.thumbnail.span4
      img(src='/img/lesson-2b.png')
      | Type folder FROM and TO copy.
  h5 Tips & tricks
  ul
    li Use only forward slash 
      code /
      | , not backslash 
      code \
      | .
    li Sure, that you finish dirname with slash. For example: 
      code C:/Games
        mark /
    li In MS Windows you should start with disk name: 
      code 
        mark C:/
        | Games/
      | .
    li You may use 
      code ./
      |  for select directory with tortigra main files.
      | It may be usefull, when you run current program from USB-drive.

  hr
  a(name='select', href='#select')
    h4 Select files to copy
  ul.thumbnails
    li.thumbnail.span4
      img(src='/img/lesson-3a.png')
      | You can select directories to copy in folder tree.
    li.thumbnail.span4
      img(src='/img/lesson-3b.png')
      | Or you may select files (or dirs) in file list.

  hr
  a(name='finish', href='#finish')
    h4 Confirm your selection
  ul.thumbnails
    li.thumbnail.span4
      img(src='/img/lesson-4a.png')
      | Click on button 
      code Finish
      |  on the header.
    li.thumbnail.span4
      img(src='/img/lesson-4b.png')
      | You should click on this button, when selection will be completed.

  hr
  a(name='wait', href='#wait')
    h4 Wait a minute
  code Keep calm
  |  and 
  code drink tea
  | .
